			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1284336">
									

<p>Then how the first shift occurred? Through shear force of Foundation's paranoia? And containment procedures would be very simple then: just release it into the world. Nobody will ever know that there is anything wrong with it.</p>
<p>This thing is weird like hell. Its core concept can be described in one sentence. But when you try to go into detail and decide how exactly that would work, it makes your head hurt. This is in essence walking paradox. I don't think I can fix anything in the way it works now without rewriting everything from scratch because of plot holes that will start to come out.</p>
<p>And I am actually happy with the way it works now. So I think I leave it as is for now, and see how it goes.</p>

